{"tid":2090626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[永續普京] 俄羅斯人批准修憲，普京或掌權到2036年","createTime":"2020-07-02T09:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T09:12:43.000Z","uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12c1757fbf532415eb63369dd30348e7cbced907","tid":2090626,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯人以壓倒性多數投票贊成修改憲法，為總統普丁(Vladimir Putin)繼續掌權並在未來數年主宰俄羅斯的命運鋪平了道路。<br />\n<br />\n據50%的投票站報告，初步結果顯示，周三有76%的選民批准了約200項憲法修正案，其中包括重新設定目前總統只能連任兩屆的任期上限。這將使普丁在其現任總統任期於2024年到期後可以再參加兩次競選，讓這位前克格勃(KGB)領導人能繼續在克裡姆林宮任職到2036年，屆時他將83歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%81%E6%88%96%E6%8E%8C%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%B02036%E5%B9%B4-11593646507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%2586%25B2%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25B8%2581%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25B02036%25E5%25B9%25B4-11593646507&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Ppmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=3f7f1990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%81%E6%88%96%E6%8E%8C%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%B02036%E5%B9%B4-11593646507</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲勁過史太林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同習帝鬥長任期"},{"pid":"7e3fb5e65f8046202f335732270edfe32b691b4e","tid":2090626,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"契哥等緊機會<br />\n<br />\n屌契弟屎眼"}]}